title: Bishop TD Jakes interview and Nene Leakes vs. Wendy Williams
itunes:title: Bishop TD Jakes interview and Nene Leakes vs. Wendy Williams
description:
Today on the show Bishop TD Jakes called in and blessed us with some words of wisdom and prayer during these stressful times. Also, to keep the good spirits up we opened up the phone lines to see who you think will win in a basketball game between Nene Leakes or Wendy Williams after they had a few words for each other on social media the other day. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to an Ohio man that is going against staying 6 foot away from each other.
